# Sheet Name: Evernote Shortcuts
# App: /Applications/Evernote.app

[Global]
> Works system-wide when Evernote is running.
⌃⌥⌘N            New note window
⌃⌘V             Paste to Evernote
⇧⌘K             Search in Evernote
⌃⌘E             Search in Evernote (alt)
⌃⌘N             Open Evernote Helper
⌃⌘⌫             Capture screen

[General]
⌘N              New note
⇧⌘N             New notebook
⌘T              New task
⌃⌘T             New tag
⌘E              New event
⌘K              Search
⌥⌘N             Convert Scratch Pad to Note
⌘⌫              Delete / Move to Trash
⌘A              Select all (note list)
⌘M              Minimize window
⌘W              Close window
⌘H              Hide Evernote
⌘Q              Quit Evernote
⌘/              Keyboard shortcuts
⌘,              Settings

[Navigation]
⌘J              Switch to...
⌘1-9            Open shortcut 1-9
⌥⌘1             Open Home
⌥⌘2             Open Notes
⌥⌘3             Open Tasks
⌥⌘4             Open Files
⌥⌘5             Open Calendar
⌥⌘6             Open Notebooks
⌥⌘7             Open Tags
⌥⌘8             Open Shared with Me
⌥⌘9             Open Templates
⇧F5             Switch to snippet view
⇧F6             Switch to card view
⇧F7             Switch to top list view
⇧F8             Switch to side list view
F5              Switch note list view
⇧⌘J             Open Tag filter
⌘[              Move back
⌘]              Move forward
⌘|              Focus on note list
⌥F10            Focus on formatting bar
⌥⌘←             Collapse note list
⌥⌘→             Expand note list

[View]
⌘=              Zoom in
⌘-              Zoom out
⌘0              Zoom to 100%
⌥⌘S             Expand/collapse sidebar
⌃⌘F             Full screen

