[Auto Formatting]
> Type these at start of line.
#               Large header
##              Medium header
###             Small header
()              Task
(x)             Task (checked)
[]              Checklist
[x]             Checklist (checked)
1.              Numbered list
*               Bulleted list
-               Bulleted list
---             Divider
